Sequencing Notes & Risks

- Revenue is live at the end of Sprint 4 — earliest responsible point, since it depends on real airports, pricing, and the booking flow.
- WhatsApp Business API approval (A-002) and flight data vendor selection (A-003) have external lead times — start procurement during Sprint 0–1.
- Supplier contracting (A-004) is a business workstream that must run in parallel from Sprint 0; without suppliers, bookings cannot be fulfilled even though the software works.
- Sprints 1–2 are the highest-risk engineering work (the dynamic, no-hardcoding requirement). Do not compress them.
- Each sprint updates affected docs and DECISIONS.md per AGENTS.md §17.
